title: Group of Iranian sports figures calls on FIFA to ban Iranian Football Federation from World Cup
description: A law firm has sent a letter to FIFA on behalf of a group of former and current Iranian sports figures urging football's governing body to suspend the Iranian Football Federation (FFIRI) and ban it from participating at this year's World Cup in Qatar.

title: Opinion: The British prime minister is not hiding 'under a desk' -- yet
description: "The Prime Minister is not under a desk."

title: Chinese artist speaks out against zero-Covid policy by wearing 27 hazmat suits in Times Square
description: On Sunday morning, a puffy, Michelin Man-like figure trudged through Times Square in New York, panting from the exertion of trying to move while wearing 27 hazmat suits.

title: America's emergency oil stockpile is down by over one-third since President Biden took office
description: Presidents don't have magic wands to make inflation disappear. But they do have a powerful tool that can help ease the pain of high gas prices: The Strategic Petroleum Reserve.
